<h4><b>Personal Information</b></h4>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;"><b>COLLECTION OF PERSONAL INFORMATION<br />
</b></span><span style="font-weight: 400;">We and our service providers collect Personal Information in a variety of ways, including:</span></p>
<ul>
<li style="font-weight: 400;"><b>Through the Services</b>
<ul>
